headline: National Health Organizations Expand Proactive Care for Seniors With Cadence
summary: NEW YORK, February 11, 2026--Cadence today announced new partnerships with Corewell Health, Sharp Rees-Stealy Medical Group, Village Medical, and Yale New Haven Health – a diverse group of academic medical centers, integrated delivery networks, and physician-led organizations taking a more proactive approach to senior care to improve outcomes, ease clinician burden, and help patients stay healthier at home.
